                                      <mn>14</mn>
                                    </msubsup>
                                    <mtext>C</mtext>

                                    <mo>.</mo>
                                  </mrow>
                                </annotation-xml>
                              </semantics>
                            </math> Carbon-14 forms in the upper atmosphere by the reaction of nitrogen atoms with neutrons from cosmic rays in space:
                          </p>
                          <div data-type="equation" id="fs-idp25204496">
                            <math display="block">
