                                  </mrow>
                                </annotation-xml>
                              </semantics>
                            </math> in the atmosphere. The natural abundance of
                            <math display="inline">
                              <semantics>
                                <mrow>
                                  <mrow>
                                    <msubsup>
                                      <mrow/>
                                      <mrow>
