                                  </mrow>
                                </mrow>
                                <annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content">
                                  <mrow>
                                    <msubsup>
                                      <mrow/>
                                      <mrow>
                                        <mspace width="0.5em"/>
                                        <mn>6</mn>
                                      </mrow>
                                      <mn>14</mn>
                                    </msubsup>
                                    <mtext>C</mtext>

                                    <mtext>O</mtext>
                                  </mrow>
                                </annotation-xml>
                              </semantics>
                            </math> in the atmosphere is approximately 1 part per trillion; until recently, this has generally been constant over time, as seen is gas samples found trapped in ice. The incorporation of
                            <math display="inline">
                              <semantics>
                                <mrow>
                                  <mrow>
