                                        </mrow>
                                        <mo>)</mo>
                                      </mrow>
                                    </mrow>
                                  </annotation-xml>
                                </semantics>
                              </math>
                            </div>
                            <p id="fs-idp12237584">
                              where the subscript 0 represents the time when the plants were cut to make the paper, and the subscript
                              <em data-effect="italics">t</em> represents the current time.
                            </p>
                            <p
                              id="fs-idm9913056"
                            >The decay constant can be determined from the half-life of C-14, 5730 years:</p>
