                            <p id="fs-idp18759328">
                              Therefore, the Dead Sea Scrolls are approximately 1900 years old (
                              <a
                                class="autogenerated-content"
                                href="#CNX_Chem_21_03_DSScrolls"
                              >Figure 21.12</a>).
                            </p>
                            <div
                              class="os-figure"
                              id="CNX_Chem_21_03_DSScrolls"
